<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Add</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: 0;
            font-size: 100%;
        }
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .sidebar {
            flex-basis: 20%;
            color: #fff;
            padding-top: 20px;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: #333;
        }
        p{
            font-size: 30px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        .mainpage {
            width: 80%;
            padding: 1rem;

        }
        .store_title{
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
            width: 1000px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .store_sub{
            background-color: orange;
            width: 1000px;
            height: 30px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        #btn_store{
            width: 200px;
            height: 30px;
            font-size: large;
            background-color: orange;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-left: 50px;

        }
        .menu1{
            /* border: 1px solid black; */
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 1000px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        .image h2{
            text-align:left;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        #menu1_name{
            background-color: oldlace;
            width: 250px;
            height: 25px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: large;
        }
        #menu1_price{
            background-color: oldlace;
            width: 250px;
            height: 25px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: large;
        }
        #menu1_context{
            background-color: oldlace;
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: large;
        }
        .image{
            /* border: 1px solid black;
            border-radius: 10px; */
            margin-left: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
            width: 1000px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            /* font-size: 30px; */
        }
        h5 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: black;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        ul li a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        ul li a:hover {
            color: white;
        }
        #btn_submit, #btn_cancel{
            width: 490px;
            height: 40px;
            font-size: large;
            background-color: orange;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .finish_space{
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<form action="/store/create" method="post">
    <main class="container">
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <p>사장님 페이지</p>
            <h5> > 가게 정보</h5>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><a href="ownerStoreAdd.mustache">가게 등록</a></li>
                <li><a href="ownerStoreEdit.mustache">가게 수정</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">리뷰 관리</a></li>
            </ul>
            <h5> > 매출 관리</h5>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><a href="#">오늘의 매출</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">월 매출</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">년 매출</a></li>
            </ul>
            <h5> > 예약 관리</h5>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><a href="#">이번 주 예약</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">지난 예약</a></li>
            </ul>
            <h5> > 공지 사항</h5>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><a href="#">공지사항</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">서비스 소개</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">자주 묻는 질문</a></li>
            </ul>
        </aside>
        <section >
            <fieldset>
                <div>
                    <br>
                    <p><img src="/static/img/check.png" width="20px">   메뉴</p></div><br>
                <div class="store_title">
                    메뉴를 등록하는 페이지 입니다.
                </div><br>
                <div class="store_sub">
                    <button id="btn_store">메뉴조회</button>
                    <button id="btn_store">메뉴등록</button>
                    <button id="btn_store">메뉴수정</button>
                </div><br>
                <div class="menu1">
                    <h5> > 가게이름</h5>
                    <input type="text" id="menu1_name" name="name" placeholder=" 하하호호샐러드"><br><br>
                    <h5> > 연락처</h5>
                    <input type="text"  name="phone" placeholder=" 010-1234-5678"><br><br>
                    <h5> > 주소</h5>
                    <input type="text"  name="address" placeholder=" 서울특별시"><br><br>
                    <h5> > 오픈시간</h5>
                    <input type="time" name="open_time" ><br><br>
                    <h5> > 마감시간</h5>
                    <input type="time"  name="close_time"><br><br>
                    <h5> > 휴무일</h5>
                    <input type="text"  name="rest_day"><br><br>
                    <h5> > 메뉴 설명</h5><br>
                    <textarea name="content" cols="100" rows="13" > 가게예뻐</textarea><br><br>
                </div><br><br>
                <div class="image"><br>
                    <h2> > 가게사진</h2><br>
                    <div><input type="file" name="photo" onchange="readURL(this);"><br>
                        <img id="preview" width="300px" /><br><br><br></div>

                    <!-- <button id="btn_addmenu">메뉴 추가하기</button><br><br> -->
                </div><br><br><br>
                <div>
                    <div class="finish_space">
                        <button type="submit" id="btn_submit" value="등록">등록</button>
                        <button  id="btn_cancel" ><a href="/store" value="취소">취소</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </fieldset>
        </section>
    </main>
</form>
<script>
    function readURL(input) {
        if (input.files && input.files[0]) {
            var reader = new FileReader();
            reader.onload = function(e) {
                document.getElementById('preview').src = e.target.result;
            };
            reader.readAsDataURL(input.files[0]);
        } else {
            document.getElementById('preview').src = "";
        }
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>


